OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,FA United States consortium has
OL,7,Ffinalised a deal to buy National
OL,8,FLeague football club Tamworth FC.
OL,10,FThe new owner, Abdullah Ashraf, is a
OL,11,F24-year-old real estate investor. He's
OL,12,Fpromised to be "hands on" in his
OL,13,Frunning of Tamworth and committed to
OL,14,Fgetting them promoted.
OL,16,FHe bought the club through a real
OL,17,Festate investment group, Dawn Group
OL,18,FInternational and plans are being
OL,19,Fdrawn up to develop the club's
OL,20,Finfrastructure and stadium.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
