OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,FUntil now, the identity of the new
OL,7,Fowners has been kept secret.
OL,9,FMr Ashraf already owns a minority
OL,10,Fstake in Toror City, which was
OL,11,Frelegated from the national league
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FThe American company already owns
OL,15,FOklahoma United FC, which plays in the
OL,16,FUS National Premier Soccer League.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
