FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,FTamworth Football Club has said: "The
OL,7,Fdramatic transatlantic deal completes
OL,8,Fmonths of intense negotiations to
OL,9,Freach an agreement to buy the club and
OL,10,Fgain approval by the Football
OL,11,FAssociation, Football League and the
OL,12,Fnewly formed Independent Football
OL,13,FRegulators.
OL,15,F"Now, the new chairman is impatient to
OL,16,Fstart planning for next season and
OL,17,Fpromises he will be a regular at the
OL,18,Fclub rather than a faraway absentee
OL,19,Fowner.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,FThe club added: "He says his main
OL,7,Fambition is to achieve promotion into
OL,8,Fthe Football League for the first time
OL,9,Fin the club's history."
OL,11,FKeen football fan Ashraf said: "I'm
OL,12,Fexceptionally excited and blessed to
OL,13,Fbe the next custodian of Tamworth
OL,14,FFootball Club!
OL,16,F"Previous owners Bob Andrews and Steve
OL,17,FLathbury have done amazingly well with
OL,18,Fthe club over the past 40 years.
OL,26,@sD@`OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"Back-to-back promotions, the
OL,7,Fexcitement of the 2024/25 FA Cup run
OL,8,Fand stabilising the club in the
OL,9,FNational League are superb
OL,10,Fachievements.
OL,12,F"Now it's time to build on those
OL,13,Fsuccesses and take the club to even
OL,14,Fgreater heights and I intend to make
OL,15,Fthe dream of Tamworth playing in the
OL,16,FEFL a reality!"
OL,18,FHe added: "I will be very 'hands-on'
OL,19,Fat Tamworth and won't be an absentee
OL,20,FownerJwatching on from across the
OL,21,FAtlantic.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@OO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"I'll be flying over frequently to
OL,7,Fsupport the club and push forward my
OL,8,Fplans to advance Tamworth FC on and
OL,9,Foff the field.
OL,11,F"I hope to quickly become a familiar
OL,12,Fface in the stadium and fans will soon
OL,13,Frealise just how passionate I am about
OL,14,Four club!"
OL,16,FHe continued: "I see a very bright and
OL,17,Fexciting future ahead and, in my
OL,18,Fcapacity as Chairman, I guarantee that
OL,19,FI will do everything in my power to
OL,20,Fpush Tamworth Football Club to new
OL,21,Fheights.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@JO]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"I've really enjoyed attending matches
OL,7,Fand visiting the town in recent months
OL,8,Fand could not be happier as we embark
OL,9,Fupon this new chapter in the club's
OL,10,Fhistory.
OL,12,F"Tamworth is an exceptional town with
OL,13,Fa beloved football club right at the
OL,14,Fheart of the community and we aim to
OL,15,Fkeep it that way.
OL,17,F"So to the club's amazing fans,
OL,18,Fplayers, staff and to the town, I am
OL,19,Fgenuinely honoured to be going on this
OL,20,Fjourney with you all.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"Together, we will bring about a new
OL,7,Fdawn for Tamworth. Come on you Lambs!"
OL,9,FDGI's Executive Senior Vice President
OL,10,FNathan Walter, who worked at West
OL,11,FBromwich Albion between 2009 and 2011,
OL,12,Falso said, "Abdullah's passion for
OL,13,Ffootball is why he is among the
OL,14,Fyoungest executives actively operating
OL,15,Facross both the North American and
OL,16,FBritish football ecosystems.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]tD@LOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"His work sits at the intersection of
OL,7,Fstrategic finance, real asset
OL,8,Fdevelopment, and regional economic
OL,9,Fgrowth, positioning him as an emerging
OL,10,Ffigure in the investment community and
OL,11,Fthe football industry.
OL,13,F"His key ownership interests in
OL,14,FOklahoma United and now Tamworth are
OL,15,Fpart of a strategic focus on sports
OL,16,Finfrastructure, club development, and
OL,17,Flong-term franchise value creation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781719875
OL,3,CNew Tamworth FC owner wants to take
OL,4,Cclub into English football league
OL,6,F"It's astonishing to think such a
OL,7,Fyoung businessman has accomplished so
OL,8,Fmuch so soon in his career and I know
OL,9,Fhis ambition and tenacity will be a
OL,10,Fmassive boost to Tamworth Football
OL,11,FClub."
OL,13,FTamworth are the latest Midlands
OL,14,Ffootball club targeted by American
OL,15,Finvestment. Birmingham City, West
OL,16,FBromwich Albion and Walsall all have
OL,17,FAmerican owners.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
